settings.title: WOW! a whole page just about me

settings.editor:
Hello there! Thank you for exploring my website.

My name is Pratham Gupta. I am currently a final year student pursuing B-tech in Electronics and communication Engineering from Vellore Institute of Technology, Vellore.

I am a tech enthusiast and definitely a versatile person. Wanna know more about me? Click the button down below.

I enjoy living in Jaipur city but get stir-crazy if I'm here too long.

Adding Progress To My Resume......

Well, I mostly like to spend my time learning new and innovative technologies or i will just have a coffee and do coding.

I also watch web-series a lot. Nowadays, mostly anime but yeah a lot!.

Next best thing that is part of my life is guitar and Casio. I love playing those whenever I've a bad day or just when I have nothing much to do.

Well I am a Teaching Assistant in Coding Ninjas, I love teaching people and solving their doubts and thus have a vision to be at the top of my field so that i can mentor others who lack skills and knowledge

Not so much. I just have a vision of having to give my parents as much as I can. I really want to make them proud !!

It's a wrap, folks!!

Okay, so if you are reading this, I definitely wanna meet you. So please check out the contact page and I will see you there!!
